data.text:
Eric Lindal will preview his new film on the history of the Thunderbird sailboat and what makes this boat so exciting and sought-after. It has almost cult-like status among sailors and boat lovers. (The Harbor History Museum has Thunderbird # 1 in our maritime collection!)

This virtual presentation will be hosted by our Executive Director, Stephanie Lile. We hope you’ll join us as we have learn about the Thunderbird and why this boat means so much to so many people.

To participate and receive a link to this presentation, please email Robin Harrison at operations@harborhistorymuseum.org.
